title: KIP-1: Governance 1.0
body:
The community has created the proposed Governance 1.0 Model. This is the first step into gradual decentralization of power in the K.I.A. DAO. With this proposal we can begin to self-govern, propose, enact and change the direction of the Agency.

Read the proposal document here: https://bit.ly/2YUT8N3

Should we accept this document as the governance model for the DAO?
author: 0x8F42b5DAdd0e7adB633910D9fA3Dc7f83264730a
